        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- About Us Section -->
    <section class="py-8 px-4 md:py-16 md:px-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center">
            <!-- Content Left -->
            <div class="md:w-1/2">
                <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">About Us</h1>
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-4">Who We Are</h2>
                <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 mb-4">
                    At <strong>Book My Ambulance (BMA)</strong>, we are dedicated to transforming emergency medical services by providing a quick and reliable way for patients to access the right ambulance, anytime, anywhere.
                </p>
                <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 mb-4">
                    Our mission is simple: <strong>to save lives by simplifying access to emergency medical transportation.</strong>
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-4">What We Do</h2>
                <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 mb-4">
                    BMA allows users to book ambulances based on the specific type of medical emergency. Whether you're looking for a specialized vehicle for a cardiac emergency, pediatric care, or any other medical department, our service ensures that you get the right ambulance with the right equipment and trained personnel.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-4">Why Choose Us</h2>
                <ul class="text-lg md:text-xl list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-2">
                    <li><strong>Specialized Care:</strong> We understand that not all emergencies are the same. That's why we connect you with ambulances based on the type of medical expertise required.</li>
                    <li><strong>24/7 Availability:</strong> Our platform operates round-the-clock, ensuring that help is always just a click away.</li>
                    <li><strong>Trained Professionals:</strong> Our ambulance partners are staffed with certified paramedics and drivers trained to handle a wide range of medical situations.</li>
                    <li><strong>Safety First:</strong> We maintain the highest standards of hygiene and safety in all our ambulances, with strict adherence to medical protocols.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Image Right -->
            <div class="md:w-1/2 flex flex-col gap-8">
                <img src="/images/about.jpg" alt="About Us Image" class="rounded-lg shadow-lg w-full h-auto">
                <img src="/images/about2.jpg" alt="About Us Image" class="rounded-lg shadow-lg w-full h-auto">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="bg-white py-4">
